title: Schleicher resigns.

Schleicher returns to his waiting ministers and relays the outcome. An announcement of his resignation—prepared weeks in advance—is released to the press.

At this stage, the options have narrowed to two: a return of Papen, or the ascension of [+ nsdap_chancellor +]. Both promise disaster for Germany—and the latter, disaster for all of humanity.

